		<td><b>NESICIDE V1.006 release</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><a href="http://nesicide.com/?s=download" class="postlink">NESICIDE V1.006</a> Windows setup.msi updated.
<br />
<br />I also added a NESICIDE project based on Tepples' recent simple sprite demo.
<br />
<br />Added PNG file import capability to Binary Files.  PNG files can now be added directly to a project and used directly in the construction of Graphics Banks.  It'll import PNG files of any size (NxM where N,M are 8n and n&gt;0), and they can be added to and arranged in Graphics Banks in any manner.  Both online examples updated to use the raw PNG files available in their distributions instead of pre-converted CHR.  For now the converter just assumes its a 2-bitplane image.  More image formats should be supportable fairly easily, I just started with PNG to prove the code out.
<br />
<br />Added mirroring setup display to Mapper Inspector.
<br />
<br />Added more FME-7 display to Mapper Inspector.  Still trying to figure out what's up wtih Batman - Return of the Joker.
<br />
<br />Big thanks to Tepples for the colorful simple sprite demo!

		

		</td>
